<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: advanced fabrication -->
  <AdvancedFabrication.label>高级精密装配</AdvancedFabrication.label>
  <!-- EN: Fabricate advanced components from standard components and other materials. -->
  <AdvancedFabrication.description>解锁用零部件和其他材料制作「高级零部件」。</AdvancedFabrication.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->advanced component fabrication</li>
    <li>subject_story->traded advanced components to desperate rimworlders</li>
    <li>subject_story->learned the secrets of fabricating advanced components and died without revealing them</li>
    <li>subject_story->balked at the extreme cost of crafting advanced components and chose a simpler lifestyle</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->fabricating advanced components</li>
  -->
  <AdvancedFabrication.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->高级零部件装配</li>
    <li>subject_story->把高级零部件卖给了绝望的边缘世界人</li>
    <li>subject_story->学到了制造高级零部件的机密，死也不肯透露出来</li>
    <li>subject_story->在制造高级零部件的高昂成本面前退缩，选择了更简单的生活方式</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->装配高级零部件</li>
  </AdvancedFabrication.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: bionic replacements -->
  <Bionics.label>仿生学</Bionics.label>
  <!-- EN: Build high-tech bionic body parts to replace lost limbs and eyes. Requires a skilled doctor to attach. -->
  <Bionics.description>解锁制作高科技的仿生体部件，用于替换失去的肢体和器官。需要一名熟练的医生进行安装。</Bionics.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->bionic prosthesis</li>
    <li>subject_story->worked primarily with disfigured soldiers, crafting bespoke bionic facial elements so they could return to their loved ones</li>
    <li>subject_story->studied slowed vids of human motion to better craft bionic prosthetics</li>
    <li>subject_story->was volunteered to have the various prototype bionics  implanted, ending up as more machine than man</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing bionic prosthetics</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->utilizing bionic body parts</li>
  -->
  <Bionics.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->仿生假体</li>
    <li>subject_story->主要与毁容的士兵合作，制作定制的仿生脸皮，这样士兵们就能无虑回到亲人身边</li>
    <li>subject_story->研究人体运动的慢速视频，以更好地制作仿生假体</li>
    <li>subject_story->自愿植入各种原型仿生体，最终变得更像机器而不是人了</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作仿生假体</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->利用仿生体</li>
  </Bionics.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: pulse-charged munitions -->
  <ChargedShot.label>电荷弹</ChargedShot.label>
  <!-- EN: Build weapons which fire pulse-charged munitions for extra damage. Note that these also require advanced components. -->
  <ChargedShot.description>解锁制作发射高伤害脉冲电荷弹的「电荷步枪」和「电荷标枪」。请注意，它们制作时都需要消耗高级零部件。</ChargedShot.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->pulse munitions</li>
    <li>subject_story->studied glitterworld monorails and modified the tech for weapons</li>
    <li>subject_story->killed a mechanical crawler by kiting it with a charge lance</li>
    <li>subject_story->learned how to imbue rifle ammunition with retained charge, heavily increasing its lethality</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing pulse munitions</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->utilising pulse munitions</li>
  -->
  <ChargedShot.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->电荷弹</li>
    <li>subject_story->研究了闪耀世界的单轨道系统，改进了武器技术</li>
    <li>subject_story->用机械族自带的电荷标枪杀死了它</li>
    <li>subject_story->学会了如何为步枪弹药充能加速，大大提高了它的杀伤力</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作电荷弹</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->利用电荷弹</li>
  </ChargedShot.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: cryptosleep casket -->
  <Cryptosleep.label>低温休眠舱</Cryptosleep.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct cryptosleep caskets, which can put living beings in a state of indefinite suspended animation. -->
  <Cryptosleep.description>解锁建造「低温休眠舱」，可使其内的生命体进入生理上的暂停状态。</Cryptosleep.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->cryptosleep</li>
    <li>subject_story->intended to test a prototype cryptosleep casket and woke a generation later, alone</li>
    <li>subject_story->sentenced the system's worst criminal to indefinite cryptosleep rather than death</li>
    <li>subject_story->used a cryptosleep capsule to suspend the terminally ill, so they could see their children once they'd grown up</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing cryptosleep caskets</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->inducing cryptosleep</li>
  -->
  <Cryptosleep.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->低温休眠</li>
    <li>subject_story->打算测试一个原型低温休眠舱，并在一代人逝去之后再独自醒来</li>
    <li>subject_story->被判处星系中最严重的罪——无限期低温休眠，而不是简单的死刑</li>
    <li>subject_story->用一种低温休眠胶囊让绝症患者暂时休眠，这样他们就能在孩子长大后见到他们</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造低温休眠舱</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->诱导低温休眠</li>
  </Cryptosleep.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: fabrication -->
  <Fabrication.label>精密装配</Fabrication.label>
  <!-- EN: Build fabrication benches, capable of high-tech projects ranging from component assembly to power armor construction. -->
  <Fabrication.description>解锁建造「精密装配台」，能够执行从最基础的「零部件」加工到组装动力装甲的各种高科技项目。</Fabrication.description>
  <!-- EN: You now have the technology to build a fabrication bench - but it also requires some advanced components to get started. You can collect advanced components several ways:\n\n  -All outlander settlements sell advanced components. Send a caravan to buy some.\n  -Some visiting traders sell advanced components. Invite or wait for them.\n  -Some quests are rewarded with advanced components. -->
  <Fabrication.discoveredLetterText>现在你可以建造精密装配台了，但是还缺乏一些高级零部件，你可以通过以下几种方式得到：\n\n-所有外来者定居点都有高级零部件出售。可以派出远行队去买一些。\n-来访的贸易商队有时候也会携带高级零部件。邀请或等待他们造访。\n-一些任务会给予高级零部件作为奖励。</Fabrication.discoveredLetterText>
  <!-- EN: About: Getting advanced components -->
  <Fabrication.discoveredLetterTitle>关于：获取高级零部件</Fabrication.discoveredLetterTitle>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->high-tech fabrication benches</li>
    <li>subject_story->spent many years crafting advanced components, to make fabrication benches to make more advanced components</li>
    <li>subject_story->traded everything to build a single fabrication bench</li>
    <li>subject_story->constructed technological marvels which the feral villagers worshipped as magical</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing high-tech projects</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->building high-tech fabrication stations</li>
  -->
  <Fabrication.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->精密装配台</li>
    <li>subject_story->花了很多年制作高级零部件，以建造精密装配台来制作更多高级零部件</li>
    <li>subject_story->把所有东西都卖了来换取建造精密装配台的资源</li>
    <li>subject_story->制作了被野蛮部落奉为魔法的技术奇迹</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作高科技物品</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造精密装配台</li>
  </Fabrication.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: multi-analyzer -->
  <MultiAnalyzer.label>多元分析仪</MultiAnalyzer.label>
  <!-- EN: Build multi-analyzers which increase research speed and allow higher-level research projects. -->
  <MultiAnalyzer.description>解锁建造「多元分析仪」，用于提高研究速度，以及解锁更高级的研究项目。需要放置在高级研究台附近。</MultiAnalyzer.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->multi-analysis</li>
    <li>subject_story->automated a research laboratory</li>
    <li>subject_story->unlocked the trans-spectrum secrets of the universe</li>
    <li>subject_story->helped identify new stable isotopes</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing multi-analyzers</li>
  -->
  <MultiAnalyzer.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->多元分析</li>
    <li>subject_story->使一间研究实验室自动化了</li>
    <li>subject_story->解开了宇宙透射光谱的秘密</li>
    <li>subject_story->帮助发现了新的稳定同位素</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造多元分析仪</li>
  </MultiAnalyzer.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: marine armor -->
  <PoweredArmor.label>海军装甲</PoweredArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Build marine armor, a general-use powered armor suit used by high-tech shock troops. Note that these also require advanced components. -->
  <PoweredArmor.description>解锁制作「海军装甲」，一种常由高科技突击部队使用的泛用型动力装甲。请注意，制作时需要消耗高级零部件。</PoweredArmor.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->marine armor</li>
    <li>subject_story->was employed by the shock troops to maintain their armor</li>
    <li>subject_story->tested the armor by walking, unarmed, through a hostile feral village without receiving a scratch</li>
    <li>subject_story->intended the armor as protection against the planet's hostile weather, but it worked well against the pirates too</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing shock troop armor</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing marine armor</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing general-use advanced armor</li>
  -->
  <PoweredArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->海军装甲</li>
    <li>subject_story->被突击部队雇来维护他们的装甲</li>
    <li>subject_story->为了测试了自己的装甲，徒手穿过一个充满敌意的野蛮部落，但毫发无伤</li>
    <li>subject_story->原本只打算用装甲来抵御星球上恶劣的天气，但它也能很好地抵御海盗</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作突击部队装甲</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作海军装甲</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作通用高级装甲</li>
  </PoweredArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: recon armor -->
  <ReconArmor.label>斥候装甲</ReconArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Craft recon armor, a light powered armor suit used by scout troops who need protection on the move. Note that these also require advanced components. -->
  <ReconArmor.description>解锁制作「斥候装甲」，一种能为侦察部队提供防护的轻型动力装甲。请注意，制作时需要消耗高级零部件。</ReconArmor.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->recon armor</li>
    <li>subject_story->led the rebel scouts against the Imperial forces, until captured</li>
    <li>subject_story->crafted powered armor light and resilient enough for the hammer-users to close with the enemy</li>
    <li>subject_story->intended recon armor more for hunters than soldiers. It sold well, regardless</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting recon armor</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->reducing armor weight</li>
  -->
  <ReconArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->斥候装甲</li>
    <li>subject_story->领导叛军侦察兵对抗帝国军队，直到被俘</li>
    <li>subject_story->精心打造的动力铠甲轻巧而又坚韧，足以让锤击者接近敌人</li>
    <li>subject_story->一开始是打算为猎人而不是士兵设计斥候装甲的，但尽管如此，它还是卖得很好。</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作斥候装甲</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->降低装甲重量</li>
  </ReconArmor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: rocketswarm launcher -->
  <RocketswarmLauncher.label>集群火箭发射器</RocketswarmLauncher.label>
  <!-- EN: Produce rocketswarm launchers, single-burst turrets which can devastate a wide area at a key moment in battle. -->
  <RocketswarmLauncher.description>解锁建造「集群火箭发射器」，一种能在战斗的关键时刻对大面积地区进行毁灭性打击的炮塔。需要殖民者手动激活。一轮连射后会进入持续数小时的冷却期。</RocketswarmLauncher.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->rocket turrets</li>
    <li>subject_story->testified about the use of rocketswarm launchers against civilian targets</li>
    <li>subject_story->constructed last-ditch defenses, including traps and launchers, in case the settlement was ever threatened</li>
    <li>subject_story->started by constructing primitive rockets to reach space, but the high failure rate led to them being repurposed as weapons</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing rocket turrets</li>
  -->
  <RocketswarmLauncher.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->火箭炮塔</li>
    <li>subject_story->就使用集群火箭发射器攻击平民目标一事作证</li>
    <li>subject_story->建造了最后一道防线，包括陷阱和发射器，以防定居点受到威胁</li>
    <li>subject_story->一开始是打算建造简陋的火箭进入太空，但过高的失败率导致这些火箭最后被当成武器使用</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造火箭炮塔</li>
  </RocketswarmLauncher.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: uranium slug turret -->
  <SniperTurret.label>铀弹加农炮塔</SniperTurret.label>
  <!-- EN: Produce the armor-penetrating uranium slug turret. It fires uranium slugs which tear through plasteel like paper, but it's less effective at close range. -->
  <SniperTurret.description>解锁建造「铀弹加农炮塔」。发射大威力和高穿透力的铀弹，能够轻易撕碎像玻璃钢这样的高级防御材料，但近距离的效果较差。</SniperTurret.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->sniper turrets</li>
    <li>subject_story->led the clean-up after the war, collecting spent radioactive uranium slugs from the front line</li>
    <li>subject_story->saw a turret shoot straight through an assault mechanoid and needed to understand how</li>
    <li>subject_story->researched the effects of ammunition density on armor</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing sniper turrets</li>
  -->
  <SniperTurret.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->狙击炮塔</li>
    <li>subject_story->在战后领导清理工作，从前线收集放射性废铀弹</li>
    <li>subject_story->看到一个炮塔直接射穿了一个突击的机械族，开始想了解它是如何做到的</li>
    <li>subject_story->研究了弹药密度对装甲的影响</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造狙击炮塔</li>
  </SniperTurret.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: vitals monitor -->
  <VitalsMonitor.label>生命体征监测仪</VitalsMonitor.label>
  <!-- EN: Build vitals monitors which improve medical outcomes when placed next to hospital beds. -->
  <VitalsMonitor.description>解锁建造「生命体征监测仪」，将其放在医疗床旁时能提高治疗质量。</VitalsMonitor.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->vital signs monitoring</li>
    <li>subject_story->struggled in an overcrowded hospital and vowed to work for change</li>
    <li>subject_story->nursed a glassworld survivor back to health</li>
    <li>subject_story->monitored the isolation ward remotely, sending mechanoids in for treatments</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->monitoring vital signs</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing vital signs monitors</li>
  -->
  <VitalsMonitor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->生命体征信号监测</li>
    <li>subject_story->在人满为患的医院里挣扎工作，发誓要改变这种现状</li>
    <li>subject_story->照顾一位玻璃世界的幸存者恢复健康</li>
    <li>subject_story->远程监控隔离病房，派机械族进去治疗</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->监测生命体征信号</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造生命体征监测仪</li>
  </VitalsMonitor.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
</LanguageData>